OL,3,CDementia care home closures scrapped
OL,4,Cafter protests
OL,6,FTwo care homes for people with
OL,7,Fdementia that were earmarked for
OL,8,Fclosure by a cash-strapped council
OL,9,Fwill stay open following public
OL,10,Fprotests.
OL,12,Fproposed closing Castle Grange, in
OL,13,FHuddersfield, and Claremont House, in
OL,14,FHeckmondwike, to offset a budget
OL,15,Fshortfall of #47million.
OL,17,FThe council said the closures would
OL,18,Fsave more than #1million over the next
OL,19,Ffinancial year, but the proposal was
OL,20,Fmet with backlash by some of the
OL,21,Ffamilies of residents.
