OL,3,CDementia care home closures scrapped
OL,4,Cafter protests
OL,6,FFollowing a 12-week public
OL,7,Fconsultation, the council has now
OL,8,Fpledged to keep the homes open. The
OL,9,Fdecision means none of their 42
OL,10,Fresidents will need to move.
OL,12,FThe council said it had been
OL,13,Fapproached by independent sector
OL,14,Foperators and it would continue to
OL,15,Fexplore transferring the homes to
OL,16,Fprivate ownership as an option.
OL,18,FCouncil leader Cathy Scott said: "I
OL,19,Fwant to thank everyone who made their
OL,20,Fvoice heard during the consultation.
