OL,3,CDementia care home closures scrapped
OL,4,Cafter protests
OL,6,F"I understand how unsettling the last
OL,7,Ffew months have been for residents of
OL,8,Fboth homes and their families. I hope
OL,9,Fthis announcement gives them some
OL,10,Fpeace of mind.
OL,12,F"Social care is in crisis across the
OL,13,Fcountry. Demand for services far
OL,14,Foutstrips resources and councils are
OL,15,Ffacing increasingly painful decisions."
OL,17,FShe added that social care "needs a
OL,18,Flong term solution rather than short
OL,19,Fterm, last minute, funding
OL,20,Fannouncements that make planning very
OL,21,Fdifficult".
