OL,6,FCllr Scott added: "We have always said
OL,7,Fthat we would prioritise local people
OL,8,Fwho need our help and support most
OL,9,Fwithin a very difficult financial
OL,10,Fposition.
OL,12,F"By continuing to run the two care
OL,13,Fhomes, whilst exploring alternatives
OL,14,Fto them being operated by the council
OL,15,Fwe believe we are staying true to that
OL,16,Fpromise."
